segue_the_chain: What else is a roadrunner born to do?

segue_dave.line: Jonathan Richman was born on the 16th of May and Paul McCartney's "Check My Machine" was released on the same day and in the same month...
segue_dave.explanation: Jonathan Richman was born on the same day and in the same month that Paul McCartney's "McCartney II" was released: May, 16.
